t;主张之间摇摆不定。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;据地方当局和联合国附属组织称，与此同时，这两个袭击国家继续轰炸伊朗和黎巴嫩，已造成数千人死亡、数万人受伤。也门胡塞武装&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/4GTGUU-ana4Z78mMHqxWj01hmeL901Xz50NxvSzz_i-2YySOuA3XqPLLqgLgv4xXffMBTuuJ-TGKsNtUu7LZMczOUvQWMbiy5emjEE99x3Y8UcSDACGUYgUecpSgTmsBkmsbTTwTZp_sfq-t0tUOl9m6Mbn9XSKaaYresTFUPB71gYYLcarsFPyNYgiynJT5wI9yRLx_uZ6GVQxwlv3hAj5ieYynMq6asKEipciP7ijZT6NAv8Wi6AWTPvxtpVC3D_RHXK89gE1q27BSzaVnKBUejKYS5mFEAqjmMUkAyhECqf4SJ_Py4seACrQImlCRE-561TQpXle2wdYKKmHzrs4TPQjE7nvh3qjpN_qrzZYbrXZxyqzxgwCZmAjaLXOmxgukxHvoSBwNFDwZaFVrtd5hpMqSR2G38IG-uYWk5DnKIWjksb6BLEkOLmKD2oJlkUMBAXNDS-mA9zxLCC4tnuCFCAMCfx1Y7JKmyUZy14cMP7SOvPH1m3oUfDz419IuKg1KmA/ZzomJtSIRr9i7w1ODh4OULAw2ZcjT_iH/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊朗对核设施袭击进行报复，胡塞武装加入战争"&gt;周末与真主党一起攻击以色列&lt;/a&gt;，进一步扩大了冲突，冲突日益集中在霍尔木兹海峡，由于伊朗&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/MblO7G96pCeV6MNOsX-SrnfeOBXxL7V4tIaB4Do-yZ9bi0yfihvLwadfExpMRNTxSDSq56H55l1J3HVmb2q81akGskFHxDps7yfWxLtBdA1CSsL3Oc5lYl3lsYtZcvU6vgpqAfs0lTyAIJcjR48JyfpwZjogcK7mD12EPYUIrcZL5KO81YRNAWBmPf8uuJHYbVCmDvuOe-Og69Fv-uFI-hc-P0HrGRNmKAUDbmqoNl5Xg3Do408fH4JUSJ65IWN0WYsJvpWogJwC6duomlN5THmQV4a3QVEbOBgI7aLnosyQOP7xT7k2ml4zB0d3-u_DlQxIWSfgdm-H-1IBmDc6HIVz-__U08SallSawhZkn8X1JAwrj6iGfLWmLAniBX_DZN-IDrwsPTLmgoNxGBU3I41-NUP5FUZyxeDjqAYRGL2QHj7C5ADG0Nk1iID3gvV41L6LqBoLPndI3qgMycVE7COmY2X_4QkJzlk22zwG0rv4q4ylhOAJRsDJ39kYh0eIfDlKaLNRUGaDfrWkkfoslHXwKQ/juI0DUzoJnvYs6lGioYtgxbwoZGWjeru/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="经过一个月的战争，伊朗对霍尔木兹的控制比以往任何时候都更紧"&gt;对这条水道的控制&lt;/a&gt;，该海峡的油轮运输受到限制。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;与此同时，布伦特原油价格徘徊在每桶 114 美元左右。如果胡塞武装再次开始攻击红海航运， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/p66toXlxcCa-X48vGTQExN2Hqt_caHc9O9Riqp9bERzLD5TF3Xoe-hsa45c-T9aBW6n3tqnJw2NHMYjArOwI18_sT384xOFgxZW_VCey1j-iapnqlzlz0uGPLSf_9HpktzSsQEUaF5jx6cguevr